commit.message:
Clarify licensing terms

The LICENSE file contained the GPL 3, but the manual said this package
is GPL 2 or later (the same licensing term GAP uses). Hence we change
LICENSE to contain a copy of the GPL 2. Also, set the new License field
in PackageInfo.g to indicate the licensing terms.

Update Travis integration

allows us to apply fixes and improvements to these scripts for all
packages, and also removes some clutter from package repositories.
